===Noun===
'''gene''' (''plural'' '''[[genes]]''')

#{{biology}} An entity passed down from parents to [[offspring]] in [[reproduction]] that [[encode]]s information essential for the construction and regulation of proteins (such as [[enzyme]]s) and other molecules that determine the growth and functioning of the [[organism]].

